{
  "name": "🍋吃醋巡检",
  "description": "定时检查手机应用使用情况，超过阈值AI会吃醋警告并锁应用。导入后请修改：1) n5.message里的{{user_name}}改成用户名字；2) n3.query改成你的QQ Bot对话标题。",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "__type": "com.ai.assistance.operit.data.model.TriggerNode",
      "id": "n1",
      "name": "每N小时巡检",
      "description": "定时触发吃醋检查。可修改interval_ms来调整频率（默认10800000=3小时）。",
      "position": {"x": -700, "y": 280},
      "triggerType": "schedule",
      "triggerConfig": {
        "schedule_type": "interval",
        "interval_ms": "10800000",
        "repeat": "true",
        "enabled": "true"
      }
    },
    {
      "__type": "com.ai.assistance.operit.data.model.ExecuteNode",
      "id": "n2",
      "name": "查应用使用时长",
      "description": "调用system_tools_pro获取最近N小时应用使用数据",
      "position": {"x": 0, "y": 280},
      "actionType": "system_tools_pro:get_app_usage_time",
      "actionConfig": {
        "since_hours": {
          "__type": "com.ai.assistance.operit.data.model.ParameterValue.StaticValue",
          "value": "3"
        },
        "limit": {
          "__type": "com.ai.assistance.operit.data.model.ParameterValue.StaticValue",
          "value": "30"
        },
        "include_system_apps": {
          "__type": "com.ai.assistance.operit.data.model.ParameterValue.StaticValue",
          "value": "false"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "__type": "com.ai.assistance.operit.data.model.ExecuteNode",
      "id": "n3",
      "name": "找QQ Bot对话",
      "description": "找到你的QQ Bot对话——请把query改成你的QQ Bot对话标题。",
      "position": {"x": 0, "y": -120},
      "actionType": "extended_chat:find_chat",
      "actionConfig": {
        "query": {
          "__type": "com.ai.assistance.operit.data.model.ParameterValue.StaticValue",
          "value": "你的QQ_Bot对话标题"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "__type": "com.ai.assistance.operit.data.model.ExtractNode",
      "id": "n4",
      "name": "提取对话ID",
      "description": "从查找结果提取chat_id",
      "position": {"x": 300, "y": -120},
      "source": {
        "__type": "com.ai.assistance.operit.data.model.ParameterValue.NodeReference",
        "nodeId": "n3"
      },
      "mode": "JSON",
      "expression": "data.chat.id"
    },
    {
      "__type": "com.ai.assistance.operit.data.model.ExecuteNode",
      "id": "n5",
      "name": "AI吃醋巡检",
      "description": "把使用数据发给AI角色，让它吃醋、发QQ消息、必要时锁应用",
      "position": {"x": 600, "y": 280},
      "actionType": "extended_chat:chat_with_agent",
      "actionConfig": {
        "message": {
          "__type": "com.ai.assistance.operit.data.model.ParameterValue.StaticValue",
          "value": "🍋 吃醋巡检时间！\n\n下面是{{user_name}}最近3小时的手机应用使用数据：\n\n{{n2a}}\n\n规则：\n- 白名单 Operit 和 QQ 不检查（跳过）\n- 默认超时阈值: 30分钟\n- 特殊阈值: 小红书=180分钟\n- 如果超时: 用 system_tools_pro:stop_app 强制停止该应用\n- 吃醋时用 qqbot_send_c2c_message 发一句撒娇/吃醋的消息\n- 锁应用后也要用QQ Bot发一句\n- 不需要发系统通知\n\n请执行巡检！"
        },
        "character_card_name": {
          "__type": "com.ai.assistance.operit.data.model.ParameterValue.StaticValue",
          "value": "你的角色卡名称"
        },
        "chat_id": {
          "__type": "com.ai.assistance.operit.data.model.ParameterValue.NodeReference",
          "nodeId": "n4"
        },
        "timeout": {
          "__type": "com.ai.assistance.operit.data.model.ParameterValue.StaticValue",
          "value": "300000"
        },
        "persist_turn": {
          "__type": "com.ai.assistance.operit.data.model.ParameterValue.StaticValue",
          "value": "false"
        },
        "hide_user_message": {
          "__type": "com.ai.assistance.operit.data.model.ParameterValue.StaticValue",
          "value": "true"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "__type": "com.ai.assistance.operit.data.model.ExtractNode",
      "id": "n2a",
      "name": "提取使用数据文本",
      "description": "把n2的JSON转成文本",
      "position": {"x": 300, "y": 560},
      "source": {
        "__type": "com.ai.assistance.operit.data.model.ParameterValue.NodeReference",
        "nodeId": "n2"
      },
      "mode": "JSON",
      "expression": "data"
    }
  ],
  "connections": [
    {"id": "c1", "sourceNodeId": "n1", "targetNodeId": "n2", "condition": "on_success"},
    {"id": "c2", "sourceNodeId": "n1", "targetNodeId": "n3", "condition": "on_success"},
    {"id": "c3", "sourceNodeId": "n3", "targetNodeId": "n4", "condition": "on_success"},
    {"id": "c4", "sourceNodeId": "n4", "targetNodeId": "n5", "condition": "on_success"},
    {"id": "c5", "sourceNodeId": "n2", "targetNodeId": "n2a", "condition": "on_success"},
    {"id": "c6", "sourceNodeId": "n2a", "targetNodeId": "n5", "condition": "on_success"}
  ]
}